{"type":"message","id":"c091db6d","parentId":"d7378092","timestamp":"2026-06-03T01:16:59.643Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6ecc46c1fca4c2d9a341905cccf\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-06-03 09:16 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\nopenclaw plugins install clawhub:@openclaw/memory-lancedb\n这个有安装吗，我看还是官方的插件呢， 并看一下对咱们现在的版本的系统是否有帮助 ，"}],"timestamp":1780449419616}}
{"type":"message","id":"aed1badb","parentId":"c091db6d","timestamp":"2026-06-03T01:17:11.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我是否安装了 `clawhub:@openclaw/memory-lancedb` 这个插件，并让我看看它对当前系统版本是否有帮助。\n\n让我先理解一下情况：\n1. 用户想确认是否安装了 memory-lancedb 插件\n2. 用户想了解它对当前 OpenClaw 系统是否有帮助\n\n我需要：\n1. 先检查当前已安装的插件列表\n2. 查看 memory-lancedb 插件的详情（如果存在）\n3. 了解我们当前的记忆系统配置\n4. 评估是否有用\n\n让我开始查询。先检查插件列表。\n\n我应该用 clawhub skill 还是直接用 openclaw 命令？让我先看 clawhub skill 的内容。\n\n不过先让我做一些基础检查：\n- 当前 OpenClaw 是什么版本？\n- 当前记忆系统是怎么配置的？\n- memory-lancedb 插件是什么？\n\n根据 MEMORY.md 的内容，我们当前使用的是：\n- memory-core（OpenClaw 内置核心）\n- sqlite-vec（内置本地向量索引）\n- MEMORY.md + daily.md（长期文件记忆）\n- .dreams/ — 向量语料存储\n\n所以我们已经有了向量记忆能力，使用的是 sqlite-vec。如果 memory-lancedb 是另一个向量后端选项，可能是一个升级或者替代方案。\n\n让我先调用 clawhub skill 看看怎么管理插件，并查询当前已安装的插件。","thinkingSignature":"48572553ae881dca585664f25d90e7b0bfcd328eee1a1b23d7c694e4f3597dfe"},{"type":"text","text":"我先查一下当前插件列表和 memory-lancedb 的详情。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vslz7pszrzw1_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vslz7pszrzw1_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw plugins list 2>&1 | head -50"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vslz7pszrzw1_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw --version 2>&1; openclaw status 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":43505,"output":408,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44027,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780449419693,"responseId":"066eb38c9ffb4157e809d25011e0e2b7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ce25b6d","parentId":"aed1badb","timestamp":"2026-06-03T01:17:21.247Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vslz7pszrzw1_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: \"Search, install, update, sync, or publish agent skills with the ClawHub CLI and registry.\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780449441245}}
