{"type":"message","id":"3ef806c3","parentId":"41657c23","timestamp":"2026-06-03T01:26:33.923Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户简短地回复\"好，不装\"。我之前问了要不要在 MEMORY.md 里加个提醒，他没直接回答这个问题，但这个\"不装\"是基于我\"不装\"的建议。\n\n这种情况下：\n1. 不要啰嗦重复结论\n2. 那个\"加提醒\"的小问题——如果他没明确说\"加\"或\"不加\"，我倾向主动加，因为：\n   - 这是真正的未来价值（等量到 X 条/出问题再评估）\n   - 不影响当前\n   - 避免未来忘了\"为什么不装\"\n   - 一两行的事\n\n3. 同时要把这个决策记到今天的 daily log 和/或 MEMORY.md 的评估提醒\n\n按 SOUL 准则：\n- 帮到实处，无需缛节\n- 不发半成品\n- 进展透明\n\n简短确认 + 主动把\"复查触发条件\"写进 MEMORY.md，不等他再问一遍。\n\nLet me check if I need to log today's daily first. The user timestamp is 2026-06-03 09:26, and MEMORY.md has the索引 reference for daily logs. But the user just wants a quick \"好的不装\" type response.\n\nI'll:\n1. Add the trigger condition to MEMORY.md\n2. Brief acknowledgement\n\nActually, let me think about whether to do this without asking. SOUL says \"不发半成品\" and \"三十秒的确认省几小时的返工\" — for a 1-line addition to MEMORY.md that has clear value and no side effects, doing it is fine. I'll do it.\n\nLet me also think about whether to write today's daily log. The user said \"好，不装\" — this is a decision. I should record it. But should I do it without asking? The user is being efficient here, doesn't want a long response. Let me do the MEMORY.md update and skip daily log (that's optional and I shouldn't ask now).\n\nActually, the existing 索引 in MEMORY.md has \"YYYY-MM-DD.md: 每日日志\" — I should create today's daily log with this decision so future me has context. But that might be over-doing it. Let me just add to MEMORY.md and keep it short.\n\nLet me read the rest of MEMORY.md to see where to add.","thinkingSignature":"65926ea8a42bfc7bb72e2db13f043422f24bd06fa21a86c8d9592f2cf2b969a1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tkkjen6ypbpk_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md","offset":1,"limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":790,"output":528,"cac