{"type":"message","id":"1f838d21","parentId":"dc53ccea","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:35:01.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户说\"清理\"，应该是指清理 capability-evolver 的残留文件。让我先看一下要清理什么，确认范围，然后做。\n\n按 SOUL 准则：\n- `trash` > `rm`（可恢复 > 永久删除）\n\n但 capability-evolver 这个东西已经卸载一个月了，纯死文件占空间，应该用 trash 而不是 rm，安全且可恢复。\n\n让我先检查所有相关的残留："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_78zjiehq890l_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/capability-evolver/ 2>&1 | head -3; echo \"---\"; du -sh /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/capability-evolver/ 2>&1; echo \"---workspace顶层是否还有其他evolver引用---\"; ls /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/ 2>&1 | grep -iE \"evolv\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_78zjiehq890l_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which trash 2>&1; which trash-put 2>&1; which gio 2>&1; ls /home/halei/.local/share/Trash 2>&1 | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":4484,"output":260,"cacheRead":57458,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62202,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780454089786,"responseId":"066ec5cbfeff07778e0ba6e6413f94a1"}}
