{"type":"message","id":"63d76c8b","parentId":"eec633c9","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:37:14.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**有装**，是**第一个**（`@pskoett/self-improving-agent`，3.0.21）。\n\n- 描述和图里第一个**一字不差**：\"Captures learnings, errors, and corrections to enable continuous improvement...\"\n- 在我们 AGENTS.md 的\"自我改进\"那一节就有引用\n- 和我们 `memory/learnings/` 目录配合用——把 LEARNINGS.md / ERRORS.md / FEATURE_REQUESTS.md 自动维护起来\n\n**第二个（@ivangdavila 的 Self-Improving + Proactive Agent）没装**。看描述比第一个多加了\"自我批评 + 主动组织记忆\"，但定位和第一个重叠度很高，**装一个就够了**。\n\n要纠正一下——我刚才看图时第一反应是\"没装\"，错的，已经装第一个了。\n\n要不要我去看一下当前装的是不是最新版本（3.0.21，3周前更新）？或者干脆直接 `clawhub update self-improving-agent`？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":223,"output":210,"cacheRead":65672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66105,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780454224605,"responseId":"066ec6500890fb4ea243a2e9ca73bdff"}}
