{"type":"message","id":"a15995a4","parentId":"93257fa7","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:50:39.183Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户要我做两件事：\n1. 升级 self-improving-agent，看它是否真的在用/有用\n2. 找一下有没有\"自动检查升级 skill\"的 skill\n\n先并行做这两件事——一个是 `clawhub update`（这个是确定性操作），另一个是搜 clawhub 里有没有 auto-update 类的 skill。\n\n但等等——我应该先想清楚\"先检查有没有自动检查升级的 skill\"再决定要不要手动升级。逻辑是：\n- 如果有自动检查升级的 skill，先装那个\n- 装完后用那个来升级 self-improving-agent\n- 这才是最优路径\n\n否则我直接 `clawhub update` 是一次性操作，没有自动化。\n\n但用户也说\"检查升级一下\"，所以他想要的就是升级动作本身。两件事不冲突：\n- 搜自动升级 skill（用来以后自动维护）\n- 同时升级 self-improving-agent（先把它升上去）\n\n我先并行查："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mumsqdytn8jn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search \"auto update\" 2>&1 | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mumsqdytn8jn_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search \"self-update\" 2>&1 | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mumsqdytn8jn_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub list 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mumsqdytn8jn_4","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/auto-updater/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":2290,"output":329,"cacheRead":63858,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66477,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780455029038,"responseId":"066ec97583d0b585da48eb1817de57cd"}}
