{"type":"message","id":"94b56415","parentId":"e972656e","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:52:48.623Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"inspect 拿到的是摘要，不给完整内容。我没法在不下载的情况下判断它做啥、对 OpenClaw 是不是真的兼容。\n\n按 SOUL 准则\"知悉的隐私，不出此门\"+\"不下注未验证的事\"，我的判断：\n- 不盲装陌生 skill（ivangdavila 那个还没看过内容）\n- **直接写 OpenClaw 原生 cron 任务**：就一行 `clawhub update --all`，没有第三方依赖，没有命令错位风险\n\n让我做这个方案。先看现有 cron 任务的范式，确保新加的 job 风格一致："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wgz77hrhzdtl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron list 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":157,"output":159,"cacheRead":73481,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780455161267,"responseId":"066ec9f933109b6a897de3ef0ac8ed1f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"49915f7e","parentId":"94b56415","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:52:51.103Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wgz77hrhzdtl_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config warnings:\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; global plugin will be overridden by global plugin (/home/halei/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/index.js)\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\nID                                   Name                     Schedule                         Next       Last       Status    Target    Delivery                                                         Agent ID   Model               \n2c9ba2b3-e380-4ca6-8f8d-f9dab9b920d9 Memory Dreaming Promo... cron 0 3 * * * (exact)           in 16h     8h ago     ok        isolated  not requested (not requested)                                    -          -\n5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6 TK选品每日9AM推送              cron 0 9 * * * @ Asia/Shangha... in 22h     2h ago     error     isolated  announce -> feishu:user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 (... tts        -"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2401,"aggregated":"Config warnings:\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; global plugin will be overridden by global plugin (/home/halei/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/index.js)\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\nID                                   Name                     Schedule                         Next       Last       Status    Target    Delivery                                                         Agent ID   Model               \n2c9ba2b3-e380-4ca6-8f8d-f9dab9b920d9 Memory Dreaming Promo... cron 0 3 * * * (exact)           in 16h     8h ago     ok        isolated  not requested (not requested)                                   