{"type":"message","id":"34790677","parentId":"29d075a4","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:57:27.301Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户问\"现在的版本用的镜像站是国内的吗\"——他在问 OpenClaw 的安装源/包下载源是不是用了国内镜像（比如 npmmirror / 清华源之类的）。\n\n让我先想清楚他要问的可能是什么：\n1. **OpenClaw 本身的 npm 包**安装源——装的时候是不是走的国内镜像\n2. **clawhub** 下载 skill 用的源——是不是国内镜像\n3. **运行时依赖**（比如 @lancedb/lancedb 这种）下载源\n\n最可能是第一个或第二个。先查一下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hxnyj4xy7l23_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npm config get registry 2>&1; echo \"---\"; echo \"npm prefix:\"; npm config get prefix 2>&1; echo \"---\"; cat ~/.npmrc 2>&1; echo \"---global---\"; cat /usr/etc/npmrc 2>&1; cat /etc/npmrc 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hxnyj4xy7l23_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub --help 2>&1 | head -30; echo \"---env---\"; env | grep -iE \"registry|mirror|npmmirror|huawe\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":81670,"output":265,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82049,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780455435413,"responseId":"066ecb0bcd736a5899f9c4d5934ae039"}}
