{"type":"message","id":"2ff11f0f","parentId":"2a53a2c0","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:57:52.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"有了完整答案。让我也快速验证下能不能访问官方源（这是判断\"国内访问稳不稳\"的真实信号）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i4zbfxpphcpp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"registry.npmjs.org: %{http_code} in %{time_total}s\\n\" --max-time 5 https://registry.npmjs.org/ 2>&1; curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"registry.npmmirror.com: %{http_code} in %{time_total}s\\n\" --max-time 5 https://registry.npmmirror.com/ 2>&1; curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"clawhub.ai: %{http_code} in %{time_total}s\\n\" --max-time 5 https://clawhub.ai/ 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":41,"output":181,"cacheRead":83816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84038,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780455464559,"responseId":"066ecb29d57e7ac3f48f499063541f90"}}
{"type":"message","id":"496de1d6","parentId":"2ff11f0f","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:57:56.506Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i4zbfxpphcpp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"registry.npmjs.org: 200 in 1.803793s\nregistry.npmmirror.com: 200 in 0.465079s\nclawhub.ai: 200 in 1.319997s"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3653,"aggregated":"registry.npmjs.org: 200 in 1.803793s\nregistry.npmmirror.com: 200 in 0.465079s\nclawhub.ai: 200 in 1.319997s","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780455476504}}
{"type":"message","id":"4568e787","parentId":"496de1d6","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:58:11.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"有了完整数据。\n\n**答：不是国内镜像。** 当前用的是官方源，且**实际访问速度完全够用**。\n\n## 详细情况\n\n| 源 | 实际地址 | 状态 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **npm 包**（OpenClaw 自身） | `https://registry.npmjs.org/` | 200，**1.8s** 响应 |\n| **clawhub**（skill 注册中心） | `https://clawhub.ai/`（看 `_meta.json` 里写的 registry） | 200，**1.3s** 响应 |\n| npmmirror.com（对比） | 国内镜像 | 0.46s |\n\n**没有走任何国内镜像**，没配 `~/.npmrc`、没设 `CLAWHUB_REGISTRY` 环境变量、OpenClaw 主配置 `openclaw.json` 里也没改 registry。\n\n## 你可能想问的几个角度\n\n**1. 速度上有没有问题？** 没有。1.3-1.8s 的首次连接响应完全够用，npm 安装本身在后台跑。**npmmirror 0.46s 是快 3 倍，但日常用体现不出差异**——除非你天天装大包。\n\n**2. 要不要换成国内镜像？** 三种情况：\n- ✅ **想换**：每天装大包 / 想装得更快\n- ❌ **不用换**：现状完全够用，且官方源版本最新（社区镜像有时延后几小时到几天）\n- ⚠️ **风险**：国内镜像偶尔会同步失败导致装到旧版本；某些 plugin（特别是 @openclaw/* 官方包）官方源才有\n\n**3. clawhub 走的官方 `clawhub.ai`**：skill 的 `installedAt` 时间戳都正常更新，没出现\"装的是旧版\"的情况。\n\n要不要我帮你配置 npmmirror + clawhub 国内镜像？速度上能快 2-3 倍（1.8s → 0.5s）。一句话说\"换\"或者\"不换\"就行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":74,"output":424,"cacheRead":84024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84522,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780455476656,"responseId":"066ecb35fdb00901fe777cd8ac68f662"}}
