{"type":"message","id":"1b48ee29","parentId":"721002df","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:05:38.645Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kjovxo0vwqcg_2","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6\",\n  \"agentId\": \"tts\",\n  \"name\": \"TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0\",\n  \"description\": \"越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略v6.0：每3小时执行阶段1（白天9-21点），S级爆款触发全流程，直接写入飞书多维表格\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1779088195684,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"执行v6.0选品流程（越泰市场趋势黑马拦截）：\\n1. 调用tiktok_product_trend扫描越南+泰国发饰品类，筛选24小时销量环比≥100%、带货视频≥8个、星级≥4.2、客单价.5-的商品（限30品）\\n2. 发现S级爆款（12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个+星级≥4.3）立即触发阶段2+3完整验证\\n3. 通过的商品调用ali1688_similar_product核算采购价和毛利率（目标≥40%）\\n4. 将结果写入飞书多维表格AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tblHU2do30jzinJT，包含：标题、主图、TikTok销量、Shopee验证数据、1688采购价、毛利率、推荐等级（S/A/B级）\\n5. 发送选品报告到飞书\"\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n    \"accountId\": \"tts\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780491600000,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780480800006,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 114732,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 8,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n    \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n    \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n      \"summary\": \"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\",\n      \"entries\": [\n        {\n          \"ts\": 1780480914738,\n          \"source\": \"agent-run\",\n          \"severity\": \"error\",\n          \"message\": \"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\",\n    \"lastErrorReason\": \"overloaded\",\n    \"lastError\": \"FailoverError: The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\"\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780480914738\n}"}],"details":{"id":"5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6","agentId":"tts","name":"TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0","description":"越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略v6.0：每3小时执行阶段1（白天9-21点），S级爆款触发全流程，直接写入飞书多维表格","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779088195684,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行v6.0选品流程（越泰市场趋势黑马拦截）：\n1. 调用tiktok_product_trend扫描越南+泰国发饰品类，筛选24小时销量环比≥100%、带货视频≥8个、星级≥4.2、客单价.5-的商品（限30品）\n2. 发现S级爆款（12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个+星级≥4.3）立即触发阶段2+3完整验证\n3. 通过的商品调用ali1688_similar_product核算采购价和毛利率（目标≥40%）\n4. 将结果写入飞书多维表格AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tblHU2do30jzinJT，包含：标题、主图、TikTok销量、Shopee验证数据、1688采购价、毛利率、推荐等级（S/A/B级）\n5. 发送选品报告到飞书"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","accountId":"tts"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780491600000,"lastRunAtMs":1780480800006,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":114732,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":8,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"unknown","lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.","entries":[{"ts":1780480914738,"source":"agent-run","severity":"error","message":"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment."}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.","lastErrorReason":"overloaded","lastError":"FailoverError: The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment."},"updatedAtMs":1780480914738},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780484738638}}
{"type":"message","id":"dccf8705","parentId":"1b48ee29","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:05:59.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"等下——我看到的信息很关键，让我先理清楚再下结论。\n\n**关键发现：**\n1. **最近 8 次 cron runs 全部 error**，但错误信息都是 `\"FailoverError: The AI service is temporarily overloaded. Please try again in a moment.\"`\n2. 这**不是多维表格权限问题**——是 AI 服务商（minimax/M2.7）overloaded\n3. **选品表是** `AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`（多维表格）/ `tblHU2do30jzinJT`（表）\n4. **最早一次成功 run（5月12日）**就明确提到过：`之前多维表写入曾报 1254302 权限错误，需要你在多维表里添加 bot 编辑权限`\n\n所以情况分两层：\n- **现在 cron 失败**的真正原因 = minimax 服务过载（连续 8 次）\n- **历史上的真问题** = 5月12日 tts 提过权限问题，需要在多维表里给 tts bot 加编辑权限\n\n我得先验证两件事：\n1. tts bot 当前到底有没有那个多维表的权限（用 tts 的身份直接调一次 bitable API）\n2. cron 现在的错误是过载还是真的权限问题（用 sessions_send 问 tts 最新一次手动跑的情况）\n\n但**用户的核心问题是\"权限\"**，所以我得用正确方式验证。让我以 tts 身份验证权限：\n\n我作为 KIIT（不是 tts）能直接看到 tts 用的飞书账号是 `cli_a930f78f51399bc6`（app_id），但我没有这个 app 的 user token——也就是说我（KIIT）能以**我的身份**（kiit 账号）去访问那个 bitable，验证权限设置，但不能模拟 tts 访问。\n\n更直接的路径：直接问 tts 当前 session。但 sessions_list 没找到 tts 的 main session（label 找不到，agentId 找不到）——可能因为 tts 的 main session 不在活跃 list 里（最新活动 1780484126 = 2小时前，被归档了）。\n\n**最直接的方式**：用 tts 的 agent id 通过 sessions_send 把消息分给 tts，让他自己验证。\n\n但更快的办法：我自己**以 kiit 身份**直接尝试访问 bitable `AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`，看权限设置到底是怎么样的——能看到该表在哪个文件夹、所有者、当前用户权限，**但不一定能看到 tts app 的权限**。\n\n我先做并行："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v3g2aizxatgl_1","name":"feishu_bitable_app","arguments":{"action":"get","app_token":"AKppbA…QnZd"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v3g2aizxatgl_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -B2 -A20 '\"tts\"' /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json 2>&1 | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":736,"output":662,"cacheRead":93475,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94873,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780484738902,"responseId":"066f3d83bd4161264a28ea4c2a1f72f8"}}
