{"type":"message","id":"5be73f22","parentId":"4cc600dd","timestamp":"2026-06-03T12:23:40.621Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，已经手动触发了一次 tts 的 cron 跑（isolated agentTurn），跑完会推送到 tts 的飞书用户 + 应该也会在 cron runs 看到结果。\n\n但这**跑出来啥还是未知**——要等它跑完才能看到具体错误。\n\n**现在最关键的事**：用户说\"改了可编辑还是不行\"——我得搞清楚\"不行\"的具体表现是什么。让我先做点能马上推进的：\n\n1. **告诉用户正确加 bot 的步骤**（\"搜不到\"是因为搜的是人/应用名，**正确做法是粘贴 app_id `cli_a930f78f51399bc6` 或者用「添加应用」按钮**）\n2. **让 tts 现场跑一次**，看具体报错（已触发，等结果）\n3. **重启 tts 飞书连接**（让 tts 立即用新 token 重连，避免老 token 缓存）\n\n让我先做 1 和 3，2 等结果。\n\n**重启 tts 飞书连接**——openclaw 的飞书连接是通过 feishu 插件 + larksuite/openclaw-lark 插件维持 WebSocket 的。看 plugins list 找 tts 用的具体配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pwvee0t46tjm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw plugins list 2>&1 | grep -iE \"feishu|lark\" -A1 -B1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pwvee0t46tjm_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-troubleshoot/ 2>&1; cat /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-troubleshoot/SKILL.md 2>&1 | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":37,"output":382,"cacheRead":100159,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100578,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780489407435,"responseId":"066f4fc0a226bde181fdce66394211c1"}}
