u: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected;     │\n│    global plugin will be overridden by global plugin                        │\n│    (/home/halei/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/index.js)  │\n│  - plugins.entries.feishu: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but         │\n│    config is present                                                        │\n--\n│ zai-provider │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ @openclaw/   │ feishu   │ openclaw │ disabled │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/      │ 2026.5.20 │\n│ feishu       │          │          │          │ index.js                                                 │           │\n│ @martian-    │ lossless │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@martian-engineering/       │ 0.11.2    │\n--\n│ claw         │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ @larksuite/  │ openclaw │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@larksuite/openclaw-lark/   │ 2026.5.20 │\n│ openclaw-    │ -lark    │          │          │ index.js                                                 │           │\n│ lark         │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ @tencent-    │ openclaw │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@tencent-weixin/openclaw-   │ 2.4.4     │","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780489423722}}
