{"type":"message","id":"4428490c","parentId":"bc6f4daa","timestamp":"2026-06-03T12:26:33.135Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`NumberFieldConvFail` ——**这说明：写入操作已经到达飞书表结构层，权限检查通过了**！只是我传的\"0\"是字符串，飞书需要数字。问题不在权限，**kiit 写权限是有的**。\n\nOK，关键认知被校正：**kiit 有写权限**。所以\"kiit 写不进去\"是我之前传 `***` 导致的假象。\n\n那么 tts 到底有没有写权限？**唯一确证方式**是让 tts bot 自己试。已触发 cron run，等结果。\n\n**现在我需要直接答复用户的问题**——用户问的是\"我能改吗\"+\"还是不行\"。我已经发了飞书消息，但用户可能没刷新，让我在这里**简洁直接**地告诉用户："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ylqn94pqhgyh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"ready to give final answer\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":130,"output":191,"cacheRead":114162,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114483,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780489581374,"responseId":"066f506e3ef2f0013d81094c314effce"}}
